10:T5dc,.page-header {
      background: white;
      padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .page-header p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    .page-content {
      background: white;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .page-content .container {
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    .policy-section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .policy-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .policy-section p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .contact-info {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .contact-info h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .contact-info p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .contact-info a {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .contact-info a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .last-updated {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-header {
        padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
      }
      .page-content {
        padding: 3rem 0;
      }
    }11:Tbbb,
    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>At ZyncSpace, our mission is to bring together chat, tasks, and scheduling into one seamless workspace. We believe that modern teams deserve tools that work together, not in silos. Our platform is designed to eliminate the friction of switching between multiple applications and help teams focus on what matters most.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Who We Are</h2>
          <p>ZyncSpace is a team of passionate developers, designers, and problem-solvers based in India. We understand the challenges that teams face daily—missed messages, forgotten tasks, and chaotic schedules. That's why we've built an all-in-one solution that keeps everyone on the same page.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>What We Build</h2>
          <p>ZyncSpace is more than just another productivity tool. It's a complete workspace that combines:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Real-time Chat</strong> – Stay connected with your team through instant messaging, channels, and direct messages.</li>
            <li><strong>Task Management</strong> – Create, assign, and track tasks with ease. Never miss a deadline again.</li>
            <li><strong>Smart Scheduling</strong> – Coordinate meetings and deadlines with intelligent calendar integration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Our Values</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Simplicity</strong> – We believe powerful tools shouldn't be complicated. Every feature we build is designed to be intuitive and easy to use.</li>
            <li><strong>Collaboration</strong> – Great work happens when teams work together. We've built ZyncSpace to foster real collaboration.</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy & Security</strong> – Your data belongs to you. We take security seriously and are committed to protecting your information.</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous Improvement</strong> – We're always listening to our users and iterating to make ZyncSpace better every day.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Join Us</h2>
          <p>We're always looking for talented people who share our vision. If you're passionate about building great products and want to make a difference, we'd love to hear from you. Check out our <a href="/careers">careers page</a> for open positions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions, feedback, or just want to say hello:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:atul.zync@gmail.com">support@zyncspace.com</a></p>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
